title: We bring a fresh air of change to your life!
posting_body: Timbre Apartments in Lakewood, WASurrounded by beautiful trees and greenery, Timbre Apartments offers one, two, and three-bedroom floor plans conveniently located in Lakewood.
Residents enjoy spending time in the clubhouse working remotely, playing shuffleboard and foosball, and outdoor swimming in the pool, playing cornhole and sitting by the fire pits.
Our community is conveniently located in Lakewood, near restaurants, grocery stores, and schools such as Dower Elementary, Lochburn Middle, and Clover Park High School.
Schedule your tour today to see why so many people love calling Timbre Apartments home.
